1
00:00:01,384 --> 00:00:03,383
See that aspiring model there?

2
00:00:03,384 --> 00:00:06,686
That was me... Deb...
until the day I died.

3
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:08,988
I thought I'd go straight to heaven,

4
00:00:09,023 --> 00:00:10,957
but there was a bit of a mix-up

5
00:00:10,991 --> 00:00:13,293
and I woke up in someone else's body.
[ Screams ]

6
00:00:13,327 --> 00:00:14,427
So now I'm Jane,

7
00:00:14,461 --> 00:00:18,231
a super-busy lawyer
with my very own assistant.

8
00:00:18,265 --> 00:00:20,366
I got a new life, a new wardrobe,

9
00:00:20,401 --> 00:00:22,769
and the only people who really
know what's going on with me

10
00:00:22,803 --> 00:00:25,938
are my girlfriend Stacy
and my guardian angel, Luke.

11
00:00:25,973 --> 00:00:27,640
I used to think everything
happened for a reason...

12
00:00:27,675 --> 00:00:28,608
Whoo!
[ Laughs ]

13
00:00:28,642 --> 00:00:30,677
and, well, I sure hope I was right.

14
00:00:30,711 --> 00:00:32,180
♪ LA, LA, LA, LA-LA-LA-LA

15
